-- Taiwan Equity Movers: Gloria Material Technology, Golden Biotech
-- B y   W e i y i   L i m
-- 2012-05-14T05:53:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-14/taiwan-equity-movers-gloria-material-technology-pchomestore.html
Shares of the following companies had
 unusual  moves in  Taiwan trading . Stock symbols are in
parentheses and prices are as of the close in Taipei.  The benchmark Taiex Index fell 0.3 percent to 7,377.18, the
lowest close since Jan. 18.  Gloria Material Technology Corp. (5009)  (5009 TT) dropped 1.5
percent to NT$32, the lowest close since April 27. The
steelmaker’s board approved a plan to sell as many as 20.8
million common shares to Hitachi Metals Ltd. at a tentative
price of NT$33.43 each.  Golden Biotechnology Corp. (4132)  (4132 TT) retreated 4.4 percent
to NT$32.50. The medical research company’s April sales fell 16
percent from a year earlier to NT$7.74 million, according to a
statement to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Weiyi Lim in Singapore at 
 wlim26@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
